description: Retrieves information about the specified service network.

parameters.name: serviceNetworkIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID or ARN of the service network.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the service network.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the service network was created, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the service network.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time of the last update, in ISO-8601 format.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the service network.

nested_items.name: numberOfAssociatedServices
nested_items.description: The number of services associated with the service network.

nested_items.name: numberOfAssociatedVPCs
nested_items.description: The number of VPCs associated with the service network.

nested_items.name: sharingConfig
nested_items.description: Specifies if the service network is enabled for sharing.

nested_items.name: enabled
nested_items.description: Specifies if the service network is enabled for sharing.
